After years of working as a curator,
SoÔ¨Åa thinks she must do something to
improve the experience of the visitors of
her museum.
After a month of testing she realizes,
thanks to the statistics provided by the
application, that the arrangement of the
art pieces in the museum is not optimal.
She reads about this new service called
iMuseum which offers the possibility to
provide users with detailed information
on the museum's artworks in a new and
interactive way and which allows the
curator to better understand customers
by providing statistics on their visits.
She rearrange the artworks.
She decide to implement it in her
museum.
She is pleased to note that visitors
appreciate the new layout and the
functionality offered by the app.
